---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - ToolVerse"
  description="Privacy policy details for ToolVerse. Our services process all calculations, formats and generations client-side without storing user data."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto glass-card p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-text-main border-b border-border-card pb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">Last Updated: July 3, 2026</p>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-text-main">1. Zero Server-Side Logging</h2>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        ToolVerse is committed to absolute developer privacy. All tool execution (JSON processing, file conversions, code compilation, and image compression) happens in sandboxed environments inside your own web browser. No inputs, codes, or private files are uploaded to our servers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-text-main">2. Local Storage Usage</h2>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        We utilize standard HTML5 LocalStorage solely to improve user experience. LocalStorage keys like <code>toolverse_favs</code>, <code>toolverse_history</code>, and <code>theme</code> are used to track your favorites, custom notepad text, and dark mode layout configuration. This data never syncs to external tracking APIs.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-text-main">3. Gemini API Integrations</h2>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        When using our AI coding tools, request payloads are sent directly to Google's official Gemini endpoint. We never store or track the Gemini API keys you input. Keys remain transiently inside client memory.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-text-main">4. Cookies and Advertising</h2>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        We do not set tracking cookies. We may include lightweight Google AdSense containers to support domain hosting costs. These providers may process anonymous metrics.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
